      "role": "user",
      "content": "self-care feels like a joke though. it doesnt stop the logic of it. if we look at it objectively, if nothing has inherent value, then there is no difference between existing and not existing. it's just two different states of being with zero net benefit. why is one \"better\" than the other if the outcome is the same?",
